A frog reminded a chick to take its medicine every night at 10 PM. One night, the chick forgot. The frog hopped over to the chick's house and knocked on the door. 🐸🐥

"Excuse me, chick," the frog said. "It's 10 PM. Time for your medicine."

The chick looked at the clock. ⏰ "Oh no!" the chick said. "I forgot!"

The frog rolled its eyes. 🙄 "That's why you have a frog to remind you," the frog said. "Now, take your medicine."

The chick took its medicine. 💊 "Thank you, frog," the chick said. "I'm glad I have you to remind me."

The frog smiled. 😊 "That's what friends are for," the frog said.
